Release Notes for Version 3.11.2
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.11.2 is the third release in Errata Tool 3.11. It closes [20
bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release includes fixes related to push task handlings, TPS scheduling and
documentation approval, CDN / Customer Portal support for updating CVEs, and
javascript refactoring for improved maintainability.

